body:
Ay guys, I need some help.

I'm going to start making videos and need your help! I have NO idea what I'm going to do for my channel name. I need a creative one.

I, personally, like names like "Evocal" and "Bryviin". Y'know, short creative names. Now that thing is, I'm really bad at that. Here's what I need your help with.

Create one of those! I'd like it to start with Z, not really resemble my actual name, and it doesn't HAVE to start with Z though. I'd like to see some creative ideas. Thanks!
